      <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-lily-500/10 ring-1 ring-lily-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-lily-400 mb-4">🎁</div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Giveaways</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mt-2">Run flawless giveaways with role/server requirements, multiple winners and reroll support.</p>
    </div>
